name: Experiment Or Die #121
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Todays piece is about the journey that we all take through life. We're never sure how that path will meander through our life, who and what we might encounter, or who might be watching. It's certainly not a straight or continuous line. It's certainly NOT a leisurely stroll through a meadow. It's a slog, uphill, both ways, in a blizzard, at night. But somehow most of us make it, but likely not alone. We all need help, and love, and community in order to navigate this oh so short period of time we have on this marble. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
